3:
MAN = 1
Append a 1. to MAN
1.1
EXP = d'128-d'127 = 1
Left Shift 1.1 by 1
b'11 = d'3
----------------------------------------
9:
b'1001
Right shift 3 times until top 1 found
MAN = b'001000.....
EXP = d'130 - d'127 = 3

